-- Bolivia’s Morales Reports Chavez Recovering in Cuba, EFE Says
-- B y   J o s e   O r o z c o
-- 2012-12-24T20:03:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-24/bolivia-s-morales-reports-chavez-recovering-in-cuba-efe-says.html
Venezuelan President  Hugo Chavez 
“is in a state of recovery” after cancer surgery in Cuba, EFE
reported, citing Bolivian Communications Minister Amanda Davila.  Bolivian President Evo Morales informed his colleagues of
Chavez’s health after visiting the Venezuelan leader in Cuba
over the weekend, the Spanish state news agency reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jose Orozco in Caracas at 
 jorozco8@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
